---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="AI for Consultants & Professional Services | Scott Armbruster" description="Deliver more value per engagement with AI-powered research, reporting, and client communication. Built for solo and small-firm consultants.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <p class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase mb-6">
          AI for Consultants & Professional Services
        </p>

        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
          Bill for Expertise,
          <br />
          <span class="text-white">
            Not Hours
          </span>
        </h1>

        <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-slate-200 mb-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto font-light">
          AI tools that make a solo consultant deliver like a full team
        </p>

        <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          You sell your brain, not your time. AI handles the research, first drafts, data crunching,
          and follow-up so you can focus on the high-value thinking your clients actually pay for.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold transition inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2"
          >
            Book Free Discovery Call
          </a>
          <a
            href="/calculators/savings-challenge"
            class="bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold transition inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2"
          >
            Take the $1,500 Challenge
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Use Cases -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-slate-900/50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Where Consultants Save the Most Time</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-300">
          These automations typically free up 10-20 billable hours per week
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-8">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-blue-400 mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"/>
          </svg>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Client Research</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">
            AI pulls industry data, competitive intelligence, and market analysis in minutes instead of hours. You review and add your expert interpretation.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-8">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-blue-400 mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/>
          </svg>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Deliverable Drafting</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">
            Strategy docs, assessment reports, and recommendation decks get a solid first draft from your notes and frameworks. You polish, not start from zero.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-8">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-blue-400 mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
          </svg>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Meeting Prep & Follow-Up</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">
            AI transcribes calls, extracts action items, drafts follow-up emails, and updates your CRM. Every meeting captured, nothing falls through the cracks.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-8">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-blue-400 mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/>
          </svg>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Proposal Automation</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">
            Feed in discovery call notes and scope details, get a polished proposal draft with pricing, timeline, and deliverables ready for your review.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-8">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-blue-400 mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 5H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v11a2 2 0 002 2h11a2 2 0 002-2v-5m-1.414-9.414a2 2 0 112.828 2.828L11.828 15H9v-2.828l8.586-8.586z"/>
          </svg>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Content & Thought Leadership</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">
            Turn your expertise into LinkedIn posts, articles, and newsletters that attract clients. AI drafts from your voice and ideas.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-8">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-blue-400 mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"/>
          </svg>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Client Intake Bot</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">
            Qualify prospects on your website 24/7. Collect project details, budget range, and timeline before the first call so you show up prepared.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Consultant's Dilemma -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">The Consultant's Dilemma</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8">
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 mb-6">
          You can only bill for so many hours. But growing means either hiring (expensive, risky)
          or working more (unsustainable). AI breaks this trade-off.
        </p>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-center">
          <div>
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-400 mb-2">Faster</div>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Proposals and deliverables with AI-assisted drafting</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-400 mb-2">Less Admin</div>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Automate research, data entry, and follow-up</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-400 mb-2">24/7</div>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Lead qualification without your involvement</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 border-t border-slate-800/60">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Your Expertise Is the Product. AI Is the Multiplier.</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 mb-8">
        Book a free discovery call. I'll show you which AI tools and automations will have the
        biggest impact on your practice within 30 days.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold transition"
        >
          Book Discovery Call
        </a>
        <a
          href="/calculators/meeting-time-ai"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold transition"
        >
          Calculate Meeting Time Savings
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
